@startuml
autonumber

participant Client
participant CheckoutController
participant CheckoutService
participant CartRepository

' 0) HTTP request
Client ->> CheckoutController: GET /carts/{cartId}
CheckoutController ->> CheckoutService: getCart(cartId)

' 1) Load cart from repository
CheckoutService ->> CartRepository: get(cartId)
CartRepository -->> CheckoutService: Cart

' 2) Convert Cart -> GetCartResult
CheckoutService ->> CheckoutService: result = convertToGetCartResult(cart)
note right of CheckoutService
convertToGetCartResult(cart): GetCartResult
end note
CheckoutService -->> CheckoutController: GetCartResult

' 3) HTTP response
CheckoutController -->> Client: 200 OK\nBody: GetCartResult

@enduml
